<html lang='uz'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Hisobni tasdiqlash</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #444;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2563eb;
        margin: 20px 0;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Salom, {{name}}</h1>
      <p>Emailni yoki parolni o'zgartirish uchun tasdiqlash kodi:</p>
      <div class='code'>{{code}}</div>
      <p class='footer'>Agar siz ushbu xabarni olmagan bo'lsangiz yoki noto'g'ri
        olgan bo'lsangiz, e'tibor bermang.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>